      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts exceptional mechanical health, with the high-pressure double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies operating in perfect synchronization. The chassis has been properly addressed with documented subframe reinforcement and a recent suspension refresh, ensuring the M Variable Differential Lock provides maximum traction through the corners. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior displays minor road wear consistent with its mileage, while the interior remains a focused cockpit with minimal bolster wear. This is a mechanically sorted enthusiast machine ready for the canyon roads.",
