      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily reliability and pride of ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, though there is light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All onboard electronics\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, touchscreen infotainment, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a full brake inspection performed last month. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears with no odd noises or vibrations. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title, perfect for someone who wants a high-quality driving experience without the 'new car' price tag. Service records are available upon request.",
